Package: hotspot-monitor
Version: 1.0-24
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Dipu Kumar dk95074450@gmail.com
Depends: python3, python3-gi, python3-psutil, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gnome-shell
Description: Hotspot usage monitor with GNOME panel indicator
 A small GTK3 app that tracks hotspot usage and a GNOME Shell extension
 that shows current speed and today's total in the top bar.
